text: DYNF (91.3 FM), broadcasting as 91.3 Radyo Kauswagan, is a radio station owned and operated by the National Nutrition Council under the Nutriskwela Community Radio network. The station's studio is located at the 2nd floor, ICTC Building, ESSU Borongan Campus, Brgy. Maypangdan, Borongan. "Kauswagan" stands for Improvement in Visayan.Nutriskwela Radyo KauswaganRadyo Kauswagan Levels Up ==References== Category:Radio stations established in 2013 Category:Radio stations in Eastern Samar
